'''Domain Yim''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Shaper caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Members of Domain Yim were extremely skilled at the Shaping arts, and they were also very devout. However, Domain Yim seemed to be subordinate to [[Domain Kwaad]]; [[Tjulan Kwaad]] was the lord of Domain Yim. One of the most noteworthy members of Domain Yim was [[Nen Yim]], [[Master Shaper]] of [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]].

Other members of Domain Yim include [[Ahsi Yim]], [[P'loh]] Yim, and [[Zhul]] Yim.

